001package doctorwhoapp.backend.data.entities;
002
003import doctorwhoapp.backend.domain.Planet;
004import doctorwhoapp.backend.domain.Species;
005import jakarta.persistence.Column;
006import jakarta.persistence.Entity;
007import jakarta.persistence.EnumType;
008import jakarta.persistence.Enumerated;
009import jakarta.persistence.JoinColumn;
010import jakarta.persistence.JoinTable;
011import jakarta.persistence.OneToMany;
012import jakarta.persistence.UniqueConstraint;
013import java.util.List;
014
015@Entity(name = "Companion")
016public class CompanionEntity extends PersonEntity {
017    @Column(nullable = false)
018    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
019    private Species species;
020
021    @Column(nullable = false)
022    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
023    private Planet homePlanet;
024
025    @OneToMany
026    @JoinTable(
027            inverseJoinColumns = @JoinColumn(name = "doctor_id"),
028            uniqueConstraints = @UniqueConstraint(columnNames = {"companion_id", "doctor_id"}))
029    private List<DoctorEntity> doctors;
030
031    public Species getSpecies() {
032        return species;
033    }
034
035    public void setSpecies(final Species species) {
036        this.species = species;
037    }
038
039    public Planet getHomePlanet() {
040        return homePlanet;
041    }
042
043    public void setHomePlanet(final Planet homePlanet) {
044        this.homePlanet = homePlanet;
045    }
046
047    public List<DoctorEntity> getDoctors() {
048        return doctors;
049    }
050
051    public void setDoctors(final List<DoctorEntity> doctors) {
052        this.doctors = doctors;
053    }
054}
